export const homeObjOne = {
  id: 'engine',
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: 'Feature',
  headline: 'Empyrial (Engine)',
  description: 'Quantitative portfolio analytics including risks and performance analysis',
  buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
  imgStart: false,
  img: require('../../images/svg-1.svg').default,
  alt: 'Engine',
  dark: true,
  primary: true,
  darkText: false
};


export const homeObjTwo = {
  id: 'fundamental',
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: 'Fundamental Analysis',
  headline: 'Fundlens',
  description: 'Fundamental analysis of each of the assets in your portfolio that gives you the best insight about the true value of a company',
  buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
  imgStart: true,
  img: require('../../images/svg-2.svg').default,
  alt: 'Fundamental',
  dark: false,
  primary: false,
  darkText: true
};

export const homeObjThree = {
  id: 'optimizer',
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: 'Optimizer',
  headline: 'Portfolio Optimization',
  description: 'Access various optimization methods (Efficient Frontier, Mean-Variance, Black-Litterman, Deep Learning...) and make your portfolio more performant',
  buttonLabel: 'Docs',
  imgStart: false,
  img: require('../../images/svg-3.svg').default,
  alt: 'optimizer',
  dark: true,
  primary: true,
  darkText: false
};
export const homeObjFour = {
  id: 'oracle',
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: 'Oracle',
  headline: 'Oracle',
  description: 'Prediction generation on your portfolio using several prediction models (Prophet, Auto-ARIMA, Fast Fourier Transform...)',
  buttonLabel: 'Docs',
  imgStart: false,
  img: require('../../images/svg-8.svg').default,
  alt: 'oracle',
  dark: false,
  primary: false,
  darkText: true
};
export const homeObjFive = {
  id: 'risk',
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: 'Risk Factor Analysis',
  headline: 'Risklens',
  description: 'Risk factors analysis that can give you a clear understanding of how to better manage your portfolio and identify diversification opportunities',
  buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
  imgStart: false,
  img: require('../../images/svg-9.svg').default,
  alt: 'risk',
  dark: true,
  primary: true,
  darkText: false
};
export const homeObjSix = {
  id: 'sentiment',
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: 'Event-Driven',
  headline: 'Sentiment Lens',
  description: 'Take advantage of market inefficiencies based on sentiment and news to better identify risks and opportunities',
  buttonLabel: 'Docs',
  imgStart: false,
  img: require('../../images/svg-10.svg').default,
  alt: 'sentiment',
  dark: false,
  primary: false,
  darkText: true
};
